data.description: Where Modern Comfort Meets Historic Charm! Step into this absolutely adorable home located just a mere 5 minutes away from the enchanting historic Granbury Square, offering the perfect blend of modern convenience and classic Texas beauty. The property greets you with a large yard and a welcoming porch—your future go-to spot for both morning coffee and tranquil evenings. Recently updated throughout, the home showcases fresh paint, new appliances, and modern fixtures, seamlessly integrating modern comforts with timeless design. Boasting all flat, usable land, the property offers a versatile outdoor space ripe for gardening, recreational activities, or future expansion. Situated in a family-friendly neighborhood with nearby schools, parks, & community events, this home is ideal for families or anyone looking to immerse themselves in a vibrant community. Don't miss your chance to make this dream home.
